{"tid":851971,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【多圖】裸模食完唱：C朗唔夠硬","createTime":"2018-10-07T13:47:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-08T16:42:20.000Z","uid":34572,"like":18,"dislike":173,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"3d98013dd4d7fd0eed62a997cf61ec2979dc9e07","tid":851971,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T13:47:51.000Z","msg":"葡萄牙球星C朗近期捲入9年前，涉嫌強姦前女模特兒Kathryn Mayorga一事，搞到周身蟻。英國真人騷女星Jasmine Lennard似乎嫌佢未夠煩，仲趁機爆料，話早於10年已經同C朗喺拉斯維加斯瘋狂床戰，當時C朗即使有傷在身，都一樣奮勇「作戰」。<br />\n<br />\nJasmine Lennard話同C朗第1次見面之後，對方就發短訊畀佢再約會，Jasmine為咗畀呢位射手一個驚喜，竟然赤裸上半身，開車去接C朗返自己屋企。不過，C朗入屋之後，被Jasmine Lennard嘅寵物狗嚇親，認真細膽，立即令女方對佢嘅印象大打折扣：「我鍾意硬朗嘅男人，佢明顯唔係。」<br />\n<br />\n結果兩人床戰之後，Jasmine Lennard拒絕同C朗食飯，似乎唔滿意佢表現。"},{"pid":"d9db2180dbd9d8e9f9f2dcaa2ee01df7c6d048a5","tid":851971,"uid":31475,"like":230,"dislike":3,"score":227,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T13:48:48.000Z","msg":"唔怪得之要強姦啦<br />\n原來太軟"},{"pid":"1cbe86cbbbc1844c07606e459ae285e9854929fd","tid":851971,"uid":47268,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T13:49:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1115ea7d82c2939d46123e3712eebf20b6123ba","tid":851971,"uid":80503,"like":52,"dislike":1,"score":51,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T13:50:40.000Z","msg":"標題黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b285698ecfee2a516dc5c5b2bfe4f72f75763fe","tid":851971,"uid":76344,"like":117,"dislike":2,"score":115,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T13:53:57.000Z","msg":"Google左，好難唔軟喎，個樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n借啲意出黎抽水咋?"},{"pid":"27b5ba06ecc98d91702ee38121da9b7eaa47fc0d","tid":851971,"uid":50060,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T13:56:36.000Z","msg":"運動員唔係性慾好大架咩(奧運村reference )<br />\n<br />\n點解C朗會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a14a056cb8